### Blueprint Research Prompt

#### [MODIFY] [system_research_blueprint_biography.txt](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/prompts/system_research_blueprint_biography.txt)

Add `dark_impact` section to blueprint data schema:
```json
"dark_impact": {
  "victim_scale": "Local_Harm | National_Destruction | Genocide_Level",
  "estimated_casualties": "number or range",
  "systematic_methods": ["list of methods used"],
  "enabling_factors": ["what allowed this to happen"],
  "affected_populations": ["who was harmed"]
}
```

Add `downfall_pattern` section (currently missing, needed for Sự Lụi Tàn scoring too):
```json
"downfall_pattern": {
  "severity": "Poor_Judgment | Systematic_Corruption | Megalomaniac_Collapse",
  "self_inflicted": true/false,
  "cause_of_end": "description"
}
```

> [!IMPORTANT]
> These sections should be collected ONLY WHEN RELEVANT — if the subject has no dark impact or downfall, the fields will be empty (which correctly scores those frameworks low).

